### Quiz API Tests

### 1. Get Quiz by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/quiz/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. Get Quizzes by Module
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/quiz/module/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Submit Quiz
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/quiz/submit
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quizId": 1,
  "answers": [
    {
      "questionId": 1,
      "optionId": 1
    },
    {
      "questionId": 2,
      "optionId": 5
    },
    {
      "questionId": 3,
      "optionId": 9
    }
  ]
}

### 4. Get Quiz Result
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/quiz/result/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Get User Quiz Results
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/quiz/results
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Check Quiz Completion
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/quiz/completed/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}} 